OL,3,CNumber of asylum seekers in hotels
OL,4,Crises by 13% in three months, new data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe number of asylum seekers being
OL,8,Fhoused temporarily in UK hotels has
OL,9,Frisen by 13% in three months, new
OL,10,Ffigures show.
OL,12,FThis comes despite the Government's
OL,13,Fpledge to end the use of asylum hotels
OL,14,Fby the end of this Parliament.
OL,16,FNew Home Office figures released on
OL,17,FThursday show 36,273 asylum seekers
OL,18,Fwere being housed temporarily in UK
OL,19,Fhotels at the end of September, which
OL,20,Fis up from 32,041 in June.
