OL,7,FMeanwhile, net migration to the UK has
OL,8,Ffallen to its lowest level since 2021,
OL,9,Faccording to figures from the Office
OL,10,Ffor National Statistics (ONS), which
OL,11,Fwere also released today.
OL,13,FNet migration, which measures the
OL,14,Fdifference between the number of
OL,15,Fpeople moving long-term to the country
OL,16,Fand the number of people leaving, has
OL,17,Fbeen declining over the past two years.
