OL,7,FThe latest figures published on
OL,8,FThursday show the number dropped to
OL,9,F204,000 in the year to June 2025, down
OL,10,F69% year-on-year.
OL,12,FNet migration peaked at a record
OL,13,F944,000 in the year to March 2023 but
OL,14,Fhas fallen sharply since then.
OL,16,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said:
OL,17,F"Net migration is at its lowest level
OL,18,Fin half a decade and has fallen by
OL,19,Fmore than two-thirds under this
OL,20,FGovernment.
